drigues}}||{{Nts|41669}}||[[Districts of Mauritius|autonomous outer island]]||{{flagicon|Mauritius}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Mauritius|Mauritius]]||[[Africa]]\n|-\n|8||{{flag|Nunavut}}{{efn|Nunavut is not accessible from the rest of Canada by road. Its entry restrictions are therefore effectively enforced with respect to prospective non-resident air travelers by federal transportation officers serving at airports from which flights depart for the territory. Returning Nunavummiut and others permitted to enter the territory are required to isolate at designated hotels in the city of departure for fourteen days prior to boarding a flight.}}||{{Nts|38780}}||[[Provinces and territories of Canada|territory]]||{{flagicon|Canada}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Canada|Canada]]||[[North America]]\n|-\n|9||{{flag|Loyalty Islands}}||{{Nts|18353}}||[[Administrative divisions of New Caledonia|islands province]] of [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in New Caledonia|New Caledonia]]||{{flagicon|France}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in France|France]]||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|10||{{flag|Marquesas Islands}}||{{Nts|9346}}||[[Administrative divisions of French Polynesia|administrative subdivision]] of [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in French Polynesia|French Polynesia]]||{{flagicon|France}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in France|France]]||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|11||{{flag|Pr\u00edncipe}}||{{Nts|8420}}||[[Districts of S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe|autonomous administrative division]]||{{flagicon|S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe|S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe]]||[[Africa]]\n|-\n|12||{{flag|Austral Islands}}||{{Nts|6965}}||[[Administrative divisions of French Polynesia|administrative subdivision]] of [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in French Polynesia|French Polynesia]]||{{flagicon|France}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in France|France]]||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|13||{{flagicon|Australia}} [[Torres Strait Islands]]||{{Nts|4514}}|