an Netherlands|Special municipality of the Netherlands]]}}\n{{efn-ua|name=fn19|[[Countries of the Kingdom of the Netherlands|Country of the Kingdom of the Netherlands]]}}\n{{efn-ua|name=fn20|Special territory of [[Chile]]}}\n}}\n\n== Entities without confirmed cases ==\n\nBelow is a list of countries and territories with no confirmed cases of COVID-19, in order of greatest population.\n\n=== UN member states ===\n\nAs of 6 April 2020, 16 sovereign states (all in [[Africa]], [[Asia]], or [[Oceania]]) have not confirmed any cases of COVID-19. Below is a list of these countries, order by population.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.worldometers.info/geography/alphabetical-list-of-countries/ |title=Population of all countries |work=Worldometer |access-date=23 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323121027/https://www.worldometers.info/geography/alphabetical-list-of-countries/ |archive-date=23 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+States with no confirmed cases\n|-\n!#!!Country!!Population!!Continent\n|-\n|1||{{flag|Yemen}}||29,825,964||[[Asia]]\n|-\n|2||{{flagicon|North Korea}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in North Korea|North Korea]]||25,778,816||[[Asia]]\n|-\n|3||{{flagicon|Tajikistan}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Tajikistan|Tajikistan]]||9,537,645||[[Asia]]\n|-\n|4||{{flagicon|Turkmenistan}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Turkmenistan|Turkmenistan]]||6,031,200||[[Asia]]\n|-\n|5||{{flag|Lesotho}}||2,142,249||[[Africa]]\n|-\n|6||{{flag|Comoros}}||869,601||[[Africa]]\n|-\n|7||{{flag|Solomon Islands}}||686,884||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|8||{{flag|Vanuatu}}||307,145||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|9||{{flag|Samoa}}||198,413||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|10||{{flag|Kiribati}}||119,451||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|11||{{flag|Federated States of Micronesia}}||115,030||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|12||{{flag|Tonga}}||105,695||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|13||{{flag|Marshall Islands}}||59,190||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|14||{{flag|Palau}}||18,094||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|15||{{flag|Tuvalu}}||11,793||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|16||{{flag|Nauru}}||10,823||[[Oceania]]\n|}\n\n=== States with no recognition or limited recognition ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+Unrecognized states with no confirmed cases\n|-\n!#!!Country!!Population!!''De jure''!!Continent!![[List of states with limited recognition|Status]]\n|-\n|1||{{flag|Sahrawi Arab Democratic Republic}}{{efn|Part of Western Sahara occupied by [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Morocco|Morocco]] has confirmed cases.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://covidmaroc.ma/pages/Accueil.aspx|title=La veille sanitaire au maroc|last=|first=|date=|website=Le Portail Officiel du Coronavirus au Maroc|language=fr|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319174334/http://www.covidmaroc.ma/pages/Accueil.aspx|archive-date=19 March 2020|accessdate=30 March 2020}}</ref>}}||{{Nts|100000}}||[[Political status of Western Sahara|Disputed]]||[[Africa]]||recognised by at least one UN member state\n|-\n|2||{{flag|South Ossetia}}<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://oc-media.org/south-ossetia-goes-into-guarantine/ |title=South Ossetia goes into quarantine |work=OC Media |access-date=3 April 2020}}</ref>||{{Nts|53532}}||{{flagicon|Georgia (country)}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Georgia (country)|Georgia]]||[[Asia]]||recognised by at least one UN member state\n|}\n\n=== Dependent territories ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+Dependencies with no confirmed cases\n|-\n!#!!Territory!!Population!!Status!!Country!!Continent\n|-\n|1||{{flag|American Samoa}}<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cnn.com/interactive/2020/health/coronavirus-us-maps-and-cases/p/ |title=Tracking Covid-19 cases in the US |work=CNN Health |access-date=28 March 2020}}</ref>||{{Nts|55191}}||[[Unincorporated territories of the United States|unincorporated territory]]||{{flagicon|United States}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United States|United States]]||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|2||{{flag|Bonaire}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.infobonaire.com/faqs-on-bonaire-trave